					<h1 class="entry-title">The Coming Dollar Downleg And Gold Upleg</h1>
					<p class="headline_meta">by <span class="author vcard"><span class="fn">Trace Mayer, J.D.</span></span> on <abbr class="published" title="2012-01-23">January 23, 2012</abbr> &middot; <span><a href="http://www.runtogold.com/2012/01/the-coming-dollar-downleg-and-gold-upleg/#comments" rel="nofollow">3 comments</a></span></p>
				</div>
				<div class="format_text entry-content">
            <a href="http://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" 
                data-count="" 
